\N<Segi>No one's here...? But I'm sure the two of them were headed
this way...

\N<Segi>That's right... Irime said she had a match today, so she
shouldn't be here. Maybe I saw it wrong...
\N<Segi>Let's go to the match venue. That should clear things up...
A

\N<Segi>...Again, I'm sure they came here, but there's no one
around. Where could the two of them be...
\N<Segi>That's right... Let's search the area a bit.

\N<Segi>...It was the same last time. What on earth are the two of
them doing in such a place...
\N<Segi>Ah...eh...!??

Segi doubted her own eyes. Deep in the thicket, unmistakably
embracing each other, were Zuuteruka and Irime.
\N<Segi>Why... why are the two of them...

Zuuteruka's hand was intimately wrapped around Irime's
waist. They seemed to be talking about something, but from
this distance, it was impossible to make out the details of
their conversation.

Irime's face was flushed. From her expression, it was clear
that she wasn't here against her will.
\N<Segi>Miss Irime... why...?

Segi murmured with a trembling voice. However, if this
rendezvous wasn't forced, she understood that it wasn't her
place to say anything about their relationship.

But she couldn't just leave them be. Because the other
person was Zuuteruka. Segi hid behind a tree and quietly
observed.
\N<Segi>Ah...!?

Zuuteruka's hand moved to Irime's clothing. Segi couldn't
believe her eyes. It was because Irime wasn't wearing any
underwear.
\N<Irime>No...

Irime resisted faintly, but eventually seemed to give up and
let Zuuteruka do as he pleased.

Zuuteruka's lips touched Irime's neck. Irime squirmed as if
tickled.

There were red marks on her neck. Zuuteruka paid no mind to
such things and continued to trail his tongue over her body.
\N<Irime>...! Ah... no, not there... mmm...

Zuuteruka ignored Irime's words and touched her breasts.
Then he began to knead them slowly and somewhat roughly.
\N<Irime>Ahh! Huh...! If you do it that strongly... it hurts...

Under Zuuteruka's caress, Irime let out a sweet voice that
held no resistance.
\N<Zuuteruka>Hehehe... bear with it a little.

Zuuteruka said so and began to strip Irime's clothes off
with practiced ease. Irime writhed, but it didn't seem like
a genuine rejection.
\N<Zuuteruka>Hey hey, looks like everything is all ready down here, huh?

Zuuteruka laughed mischievously and slipped his finger into
Irime's private parts.
\N<Irime>Ahn!

\N<Zuuteruka>Hehehe, amazing, huh? Just a little touch and you're already
like this?

Zuuteruka said admiringly. His gaze was fixed on Irime's
crotch, where preparations to receive a man were already
complete.

Irime's body began to tremble slightly. She looked anxious
as she spoke.
\N<Irime>So, um... we're going to do it here...?

\N<Zuuteruka>Of course. Did you think I'd carry you to a freshly washed
white bed or something? Get a grip on reality.
\N<Irime>...

\N<Zuuteruka>Well, leave it to me. No matter where we are, I'll make you
feel good in no time.
\N<Segi>No... I can't watch any more...

Segi turned her eyes away from the scene before her. She
shouldn't intrude any further. Her heart was sounding the
alarm.
\N<Segi>Let's go...
B
